# Authors and Contributors

## Primary Authors

**XNet Inc.**  
**Joshua S. Doucette** - Lead Developer and Architect

## Project History

This project was originally derived from the MCP Server for Grafana
(https://github.com/grafana/mcp-grafana) developed by Grafana Labs
and licensed under Apache License 2.0.

The current codebase has been substantially modified and extended by
XNet Inc. and Joshua S. Doucette, including:

- Complete CRUD operations for all NetBird API resources
- Advanced policy management with validation and formatting
- Group consolidation and dependency workflows
- Helper functions for common administrative tasks
- Comprehensive error handling and retry strategies
- Property-based testing with 100+ iterations
- Extensive documentation (1200+ lines)
- Network resources and routing management
- Port allocation management
- Posture check management

